Vue Best Practices:

Use the Composition API for better code organization and reusability
Implement proper reactivity with ref and reactive
Utilize Vue's built-in performance tools for optimization
Follow Vue's style guide for consistent code quality
Implement proper error handling and logging

GSAP Best Practices:

Use GSAP's timeline for complex animations to improve performance
Leverage GSAP's built-in easing functions for smooth animations
Optimize animations by using GSAP's lazy loading feature
Implement proper animation cleanup to prevent memory leaks
Use GSAP's stagger functionality for efficient batch animations

@activetheory/split-text Best Practices:

Use split-text for efficient text manipulation and animation
Implement proper cleanup of split-text instances to prevent memory leaks
Optimize performance by caching split-text results when possible
Ensure accessibility by maintaining proper text structure after splitting